OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FThe NHS in Cornwall has declared a
OL,7,Fcritical incident and issued an urgent
OL,8,Fwarning to residents due to "sustained
OL,9,Fpressure" on the Royal Cornwall
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,FThe incident was announced on 3
OL,13,FJanuary, following continuous pressure
OL,14,Fon the hospital's accident and
OL,15,Femergency department (A&E) throughout
OL,16,Fthe week, which saw a high number of
OL,17,Fambulances left waiting outside.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
