OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FIt allows the NHS to take "additional,
OL,7,Fimmediate steps to create capacity,
OL,8,Fdischarge patients, relieve pressure
OL,9,Fon (the) emergency department and
OL,10,Frelease ambulances and their crews",
OL,11,Faccording to NHS Cornwall and Isles of
OL,12,FScilly Integrated Care Board (ICB).
OL,14,FIt comes after health bosses warned
OL,15,Ffreezing temperatures at the beginning
OL,16,Fof January could put additional strain
OL,17,Fon the NHS, with a four-fold increase
OL,18,Fin people being admitted for flu
OL,19,Fnationally.
