OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FKate Shields, the ICB's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, said: "We are currently
OL,8,Fseeing a high number of ambulances
OL,9,Fwaiting outside the Royal Cornwall
OL,10,FHospital and of patients in our
OL,11,Femergency department.
OL,13,F"There are also a large number of
OL,14,Fpatients in Cornwall's hospitals who
OL,15,Fare medically fit to be discharged but
OL,16,Fare awaiting the right care.
OL,18,F"We urgently need the public's support
OL,19,Fto make sure we can see those who are
OL,20,Fsickest and have the greatest need.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
