OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,F"Please only come to the emergency
OL,7,Fdepartment if you have a life or limb-
OL,8,Fthreatening emergency. Other NHS
OL,9,Fservices are available, and we
OL,10,Fencourage you to use them whenever
OL,11,Fpossible. These include our network of
OL,12,Fminor injury units, our urgent
OL,13,Ftreatment centre at West Cornwall
OL,14,FHospital, out-of-hours GP services,
OL,15,Flocal pharmacies and NHS 111."
OL,17,FPeople in Cornwall are also being
OL,18,Fasked to help support the NHS by
OL,19,Foffering to support someone who is
OL,20,Fcurrently unable to leave hospital as
OL,21,Fthey are waiting for home care.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
