OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FAnybody who thinks they may be able to
OL,7,Fsupport their friend, family or
OL,8,Fneighbour by temporarily taking them
OL,9,Fin is being urged to get in touch.
OL,11,FKate Shields said: "Fast access one-
OL,12,Foff grants are available, to use
OL,13,Ftowards paying for care, expenses or
OL,14,Fequipment to help you get a relative
OL,15,For friend home from hospital. If you
OL,16,Fcould support someone in your home, or
OL,17,Fin their own home, with a little extra
OL,18,Fhelp, please speak to the nurse in
OL,19,Fcharge on the ward.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
