OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,F"Getting someone home a day or two
OL,7,Fsooner will mean we can free up a
OL,8,Fvital hospital bed for someone else in
OL,9,Furgent need ` please help us if you
OL,10,Fcan."
OL,12,FTamsyn Anderson, chief operating
OL,13,Fofficer for Cornwall Partnership NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust, said: "The system
OL,15,Fhas declared a critical incident and
OL,16,Fwhat that means is that we're
OL,17,Fexperiencing really high levels of
OL,18,Fdemand, so we're seeing more people
OL,19,Fadmitted to the acute hospital with
OL,20,Facute medical and surgical needs than
OL,21,Fwe're able to discharge.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
