OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1736085642
OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,F"So we need to do everything as a
OL,7,Fsystem to be able to make sure that
OL,8,Feverybody that has the acute medical
OL,9,Fneeds can get access to the services
OL,10,Fthat they needs."
OL,12,FAndrew George, the Liberal Democrat MP
OL,13,Ffor West Cornwall & The Isles of
OL,14,FScilly has said the critical incident
OL,15,Fis the result of a "decade of
OL,16,Funderinvestment" in the hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
