OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FMr George said: "You have a set of
OL,7,Fcircumstances where you have north of
OL,8,F95% bed occupancy even during
OL,9,Fpeacetime. And so when you get winter
OL,10,Fcrisis like this, it's inevitable that
OL,11,Fthe system fails and that can be
OL,12,Fpredicted and therefore what we need
OL,13,Fis investment in the capacity of that
OL,14,Fhospital."
OL,16,FHe added that Cornwall's NHS is also
OL,17,Fadditionally stretched due to the
OL,18,Fgeography of the Duchy.
OL,26,@vD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
