OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1736085642
OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FMr George said: "The problem for the
OL,7,Fgeography of Cornwall issue, of
OL,8,Fcourse, you can't call on support
OL,9,Fservices from the north or the south
OL,10,Fto the west, and so if those who live
OL,11,Fat Land's End and the Isles of Scilly
OL,12,Fin the far west in my constituency,
OL,13,Fthere's 100 miles of only just one
OL,14,Fhospital, which they're dependent upon
OL,15,Fand when that hospital is struggling,
OL,16,FI mean, clearly it exposes the frailty
OL,17,Fof the service."
OL,26,@nD@QOU
