OL,3,CNHS in Cornwall declares critical
OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FDebbie Gilbert, CEO, of Healthwatch
OL,7,FCornwall said she does not believe
OL,8,Fthat extra funding will solve the
OL,9,Fissue within the NHS in Cornwall.
OL,11,F"But funding is critical and capacity
OL,12,Fis a big issue", she added.
OL,14,F"We just don't have the capacity, but
OL,15,Fthis is definitely not the first time
OL,16,Fwe're hearing this. We knew winter was
OL,17,Fcoming, there have been plans.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
