OL,4,Cincident due to 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,F"But I think this is the most
OL,7,Fresponsible thing that the NHS could
OL,8,Fhave done, is to declare the system
OL,9,Fcritical incident because it tells
OL,10,Fpeople, 'look, we're at a breaking
OL,11,Fpoint and only come here if you have
OL,12,Fto', but there is help out there.
OL,13,FThere is definitely help out there to
OL,14,Fyour pharmacies through 111," she said.
OL,16,FThe NHS in Cornwall has issued advice
OL,17,Ffor those with a medical issue:
